.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>전제 조건</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>항목</th>\n<th>내용</th>\n<th>버전</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>운영체제</td>\n<td>macOS</td>\n<td>(Catalina 10.15.7)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>브라우저</td>\n<td>Google Chrome</td>\n<td>92.0.4515.159(공식 빌드) (x86_64)</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">환경이 다른 경우, 글의 내용이 도움이 되지 않을 수 있음</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"한-줄-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%9C-%EC%A4%84-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"한 줄 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>한 줄 요약</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>크롬 브라우저의 ‘PIP(Picture-In-Picture) 모드’ 를 활용하면 된다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"방법1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%951\" aria-label=\"방법1 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>방법1</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>우선, PIP 모드로 보고자 하는 유튜브 영상을 재생한다.</li>\n<li>영상의 화면 부분에 마우스 커서를 올리고 우클릭을 2번 한다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>우클릭 후에 나온 메뉴에서 ‘PIP 모드’ 를 찾아 클릭한다.</p>\n<details><summary>참고 사진</summary>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 209px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 88.9952153110048%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pip mode\"\n        title=\"pip mode\"\n        src=\"/static/bd314b8d303c48816b8a7c43d0d69478/e91cc/pip-mode.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bd314b8d303c48816b8a7c43d0d69478/e91cc/pip-mode.png 209w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 209px) 100vw, 209px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</details>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"방법2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%B0%A9%EB%B2%952\" aria-label=\"방법2 permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>방법2</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>‘방법1’ 과 마찬가지로, 보고자 하는 유튜브 영상을 재생한다.</li>\n<li>\n<p>브라우저 주소창 오른쪽에 있는 플레이리스트 아이콘을 클릭한다.</p>\n<details><summary>참고 사진</summary>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 600px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAABCAYAAADeko4lAAAACXBIWXMAAAsTAAALEwEAmpwYAAAASElEQVQI12NwdnH/7+bm+d/d3eu/sbHZ/8LC4v8HDhz8P3nyVDDfyMgUTCNjkJiFpc1/R2u7/wkBwf9DQsL/Ozg4//f09P0PAAktJZ48uw2AAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"playlist icon\"\n        title=\"playlist icon\"\n        src=\"/static/74337a2ac5e44592b86dc6cf2f05e32f/0a47e/playlist-icon.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/74337a2ac5e44592b86dc6cf2f05e32f/5a46d/playlist-icon.png 300w,\n/static/74337a2ac5e44592b86dc6cf2f05e32f/0a47e/playlist-icon.png 600w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</details>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>PIP 모드로 재생하고자 하는 영상을 찾아, PIP 아이콘을 클릭한다.</p>\n<details><summary>참고 사진</summary>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 400px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 47%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"pip icon\"\n        title=\"pip icon\"\n        src=\"/static/9db7c580521e60968524ba96af39ad11/e17e5/pip-icon.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9db7c580521e60968524ba96af39ad11/5a46d/pip-icon.png 300w,\n/static/9db7c580521e60968524ba96af39ad11/e17e5/pip-icon.png 400w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n</details>\n</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"title":"유튜브 영상을 따로 띄워서 보는 법","tags":["Tip"],"date":"August 25, 2021"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Memory Store/Tips/유튜브 영상을 따로 띄워서 보는 법/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Experience Storage/TIL/2021/08/22~28/20210824-til/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"20210824-TIL","category":"TIL","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Memory Store/Tips/파이썬에서 많은 입력을 빠르게 받는 법/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"파이썬에서 많은 입력을 빠르게 받는 법","category":"Tips","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","4018478212"]}